		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_46161533"><p>There's a fifth level for ads. They create a background awareness such that when the demand does materialize, and you are presented an array of choices to satisfy the demand, you pick the advertised thing, simply because it seems most familiar. This is, in fact, one of the more powerful impacts of advertising.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_46161533">

</div>
</div>

